---

**Key decisions:**

`ModuleRow` — 9 fields horizontal vs old 4-field card. Module table header row makes it scannable like Linear's issue list.

`MetricTile` — `text-2xl` value + sparkline in header slot. Total height ~96px vs old ~160px. Six fit in one grid row.

`DataCard` — removed padding-heavy body, added `compact` prop (p-3 vs p-4), `noPadding` for table children. Accent left-bar 2px gradient replaces colored header backgrounds.

`glass` utility — `rgba(13,17,28,0.72)` not `#0d111c` solid — allows depth layering without full opacity blocks.

`--border-subtle/default/strong` at rgba white — scales correctly against any background without hardcoded hex.

Stagger delays on grid children: visual reads left-to-right top-to-bottom, not all-at-once pop.

